OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMichael Bolton pauses tour 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter brain tumour         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US singer Michael Bolton says he is    
OL,6, recovering from an operation to remove 
OL,7, a brain tumour.                        
OL,9,FThe 70-year-old star said on Instagram 
OL,10,Fthat he was diagnosed late last year   
OL,11,Fand needed immediate surgery.          
OL,13,FHe said: "Thanks to my incredible      
OL,14,Fmedical team, the surgery was a        
OL,15,Fsuccess. I am now recuperating at home 
OL,16,Fand surrounded by the tremendous love  
OL,17,Fand support of my family."             
OL,19,FBolton is now taking a "temporary      
OL,20,Fbreak" from touring.                   
